captions.text: I ALWAYS COME HERE TO STUDY BECAUSE NO ONE'S AROUND.
ESPECIALLY IN THE EVENING LIKE THIS.
>>RIGHT, YEAH, WELL THANK YOU SO MUCH
I'M SURE YOU KNOW A LOT MORE ABOUT CHEMISTRY THAN I DO.
>>UM, NOTHING, LET'S JUST START WITH CHAPTER TWO.
PROFESSOR WANTED US TO LEARN HOW TO
>>YEAH, I NEED TO GO OVER THAT.
>>NO, I HAVE NO IDEA WHO THAT GUYS IS.
I DON'T KNOW WHAT YOU THINK THIS IS.
LET'S JUST IGNORE HIM SO WE CAN GET SOME STUDYING DONE.
WE ARE TRYING TO STUDY, SO PLEASE STOP PLAYING MUSIC.
>>NOT REALLY A VIOLIN? ITS A BROOM.
BIT IF CAN YOU JUST LEAVE AND COME BACK WHEN WE'RE NOT HERE,
>>DO YOU THINK WHAT HE SAID IS TRUE?
>>OH, I DON'T KNOW WHAT THAT GUY WAS TALKING ABOUT.
HE WAS PROBABLY JUST TALKING ABOUT THE CHEMISTRY   BOOK.
>>I CAN TURN A VACUUM HOSE INTO A FLOWER.
>>I WANT TO SPEAK WITH YOUR MANAGER.
WHY DOES HE KEEP COMING BACK!
IT'S NOT LIKE THERE'S NOWHERE ELSE FOR HIM
EXCUSE ME THERE'S A PROBLEM WITH ONE
ARE YOU ARE YOU BEING SERIOUS RIGHT NOW?
WHY DIDN'T YOU GET YOUR MANAGER?
>>WELL WHITNEY, I HOPE YOU LIKE THIS.
HONESTLY, I'VE LIKED YOU EVER SINCE THE FIRST DAY OF CLASS
WHEN YOU RAISED YOUR HAND TO ANSWER A QUESTION.
I DIDN'T KNOW YOU WERE INTERESTED.
>>LOOKS LIKE MY WORK HERE IS DONE!
SO GUYS. ANOTHER CHARACTER FROM JAMES.
COMMENT BELOW AND LET US KNOW.
AND MAYBE I'LL JUST DO A WHOLE BUNCH MORE CHARACTERS.
